title: Nike Phantom GX Pro Dynamic Fit FG
subtitle: Firm-Ground Soccer Cleats
short_description: Serious about your game? Pro cleats are for the pinpoint passer who can curl the ball around the defense and the inventive, yet elusive yo-yo dribbler who has the ball on a string. Your game is all about precision, making the plays that matter most. Take your skills to the next level with some of Nike’s greatest innovations, like an enlarged touch zone up top. It complements a design that moves with your natural on-field flow, so you can command the game from any position. This version has a Dynamic Fit collar, which wraps your ankle in soft, stretchy fabric for a secure feel.﻿
